セリアとサディのルール

1. Celia must obtain the 4-digit pin by \c[27]some method\c[0]. 2.
Once 1 is completed, she must dispel the magic of the cell where
Hayato is imprisoned. 3. She can investigate anywhere she can
reach at that point. 4. Contact from Sadi is \c[27]free\c[0] unless
Hayato's magic is gone.

5. If she absolutely cannot figure out the pin, she can learn one
digit by listening to one of Sadi's requests \c[27]\c[0].
(On second thought... hasn't some part subtly changed...?)
ハヤトとメリルのルール

1. Merill will monitor Hayato. 2. She should wait in the cage
until the code is decrypted. She can do as she pleases. 3. Hayato
can provide support\c[27] from within the cage\c[0]. 4. Direct
attacks on each other are prohibited.

5. \c[27] Any direct physical contact from \c[0] Merill to Hayato is
prohibited.

In this game, as you examine objects, the characters' actions and
monologues will be displayed in the lower left window.

Not just comments based on the simple atmosphere, but even things
that affect actual status and \c[27]heart\c[0]....

Changes in \c[27]heart\c[0] can be viewed from the menu's [\c[14]Two
Hearts\c[0]]. (You can switch with the keyboard's [←][→])

Please be careful and check regularly as Hayato may be seduced by
Merill while Celia is investigating.

And in this work, depending on the degree of corruption and the
choices accepted, \c[14]casual conversations\c[0] will slightly
change.

We recommend not using Ctrl skip as much as possible in the first
round.
